job.JobDescription:
Come join the fastest growing brand in the automotive industry! Agincourt Nissan is looking for motivated, customer oriented individuals for one of the Top Nissan dealership located in Scarborough. If you are outgoing and energetic and have the ability to work effectively in a team atmosphere we want to meet you.
Responsibilities:
Facilitates the customer buying experience with exceptional customer service;
Conducts vehicle delivery process;
Offers and accompanies customers on test drives;
Establishes strong knowledge of all products, services and accessory packages available.
Work with the sales team efficiently and effectively to generate maximum business opportunity
We offer:
Great showroom traffic and a great selection of new and pre-owned vehicles to sell from.
Ongoing training and growth opportunities;
Potential for advancement throughout our organization;
Benefit plan offering medical, dental and more.
Requirements:
A great work ethic with excellent customer service skills;
Customer Service experience preferred;
High School degree or equivalent preferred;
Valid G driver’s license.
A great working environment plus the chance to grow with a brand that is becoming the fastest growing brand in Canada. You can email me your resume and any received will be held in confidence. I look forward to hearing from you.
Sincerely,
Sunny Singh
General Sales Manager
Agincourt Nissan.
